As far as I can tell, the original idea was Daniel Barlow's.

The interface is heavily influenced by brainstorming on
irc.freenode.et channel #lisp by at least:

 Daniel Barlow
 Christophe Rhodes
 Erik Enge
 Brian Spilsbuty
 Stig E Sandoe

Those interested in the other ideas that came up can check up on:
http://tunes.org/~nef/logs/lisp/03.11.13.
